
# Heart Disease Prediction Web App

A Flask-based web application that predicts heart disease risk using machine learning. Users can input their health metrics through a simple web interface and receive an immediate prediction about their heart disease risk.

## Getting Started

To get a copy of this project on your local machine:

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/JohnEvansOkyere/Flask-App-HearDiseasesPrediction-.git
Navigate to the project directory:

bash
cd Flask-App-HearDiseasesPrediction-
The project contains:

Flask backend (Python)

HTML/CSS frontend

Pre-trained machine learning model

Sample heart disease dataset